= A change in the weather

The fuente's envelope this month is shorter than usual, and colder: the file on the Movement has been moved to a different desk — one that does not open investigations, only closes them. The security men who used to photograph your doorways have been replaced by men who do not carry cameras.

In this Republic the line between the political police and the traffickers was always a courtesy fiction; the DFS licenses the narcos and the narcos lend the DFS their pistoleros, and the arrangement has a spare capacity that is now, the envelope suggests, being pointed at you. This is how the dirty war ends an organization it has decided to end: not with a decree, but with a series of ordinary crimes that no one will ever be charged with.

**Lower the temperature — cut the expediente, ease the represión — or the leadership begins to die, one by one.** The El camino and the memorial both hang on what you do in the next year. You have been warned the only way this state ever warns anyone: quietly, and once.

- @entendido: Understood. Continuar.
- @refugio: Send the most burned names up the mountain. The sierra hides what the city cannot.

