unavailable-subtitle: Moving the leadership without trusted cadres to run the routes is delivering them by courier.
on-arrival: refugio_sierra = 1; refugio_time = time; expediente -= 8; advisor_action_timer = 12; unity -= 2

It is done the old way: one by one, over weeks, by routes that exist in no notebook. A teacher goes to visit relatives; an ex-railwayman takes a construction job in another state; a señora who has been arrested fifty-eight times simply is not home, indefinitely. Where they actually are, fewer than five people know, and the five do not know each other.

The Movement runs shallower without them — a year, maybe more, of decisions made by seconds-in-command. But the men who do not carry cameras will spend that year photographing empty doorways, and the leadership will come down the mountain alive, which is the entire point of mountains.

@entendido
go-to: post_event

The circular to the cells is three words: *bajen el perfil.* Lower the profile. Whether the organization can, having climbed this high, is the question the next months will answer in the only currency that counts.
